</code></synopsis>
<p>Checks whether @self is being currently painted by a <link xref="Clutter.Clone">Clutter.Clone</link></p><p>This function is useful only inside the ::paint virtual function
implementations or within handlers for the <link xref="Clutter.Actor-paint">Clutter.Actor::paint</link>
signal</p><p>This function should not be used by applications</p><p>by a <link xref="Clutter.Clone">Clutter.Clone</link>, and False otherwise</p>

<table>
<tr>
<td><p>Returns :</p></td>
<td><p>True if the <link xref="Clutter.Actor">Clutter.Actor</link> is currently being painted</p></td>
</tr>
</table>
